workflow.description: All Sales Orders require one level of approval from the Revenue Analyst or Revenue Manager roles. If the Sales Order is over $100,000 it requires another level of approval from someone in the Revenue Manager role who WAS NOT the first approver.
workflow.name: GWR Amp |SO Approval V2 - for prod 2 23

initcondition.formula: "User Role" IN ("Role1","Role2","Role3") OR "Workflow:First Approver (SO) (2)" IN ("Current User")
